Poisonous weeds?

606
00:26:51,290 --> 00:26:53,290
You mean these are poisonous weeds?

607
00:26:53,330 --> 00:26:55,370
How are they different from wild vegetables?

608
00:26:55,370 --> 00:26:56,950
This thing is called daylily.

609
00:26:56,950 --> 00:26:59,310
When I was little and went herb-picking with my father,

610
00:26:59,310 --> 00:27:00,240
