612
00:27:02,060 --> 00:27:03,320
It's hallucinogenic,

613
00:27:03,730 --> 00:27:05,840
and it can cause drastic changes in behavior for those who accidentally ingest it,

614
00:27:05,840 --> 00:27:08,370
making them act completely out of character.

615
00:27:13,520 --> 00:27:14,250
What's wrong?

616
00:27:14,250 --> 00:27:15,910
Do you want to be poisoned too?

617
00:27:16,750 --> 00:27:19,210
We don't have time to take care of you as well.

618
00:27:20,710 --> 00:27:22,370
