619
00:27:22,370 --> 00:27:23,790
Do we need to call a doctor?

620
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:24,570
Don't worry.

621
00:27:25,100 --> 00:27:27,810
There is actually a kind of herb that can detoxify this poison.

622
00:27:27,810 --> 00:27:29,150
Its name is woad.

623
00:27:29,630 --> 00:27:31,270
When I was little, my father and I

624
00:27:31,270 --> 00:27:33,330
