629
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:45,150
Woad...

630
00:27:45,190 --> 00:27:46,230
Woad...

631
00:27:46,490 --> 00:27:47,130
Eleven.

632
00:27:47,250 --> 00:27:48,830
