633
00:27:49,070 --> 00:27:51,270
I'll go to the mountains and look for it.

634
00:27:51,620 --> 00:27:52,090
Alright.

635
00:27:52,090 --> 00:27:53,190
Forget it.

636
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:54,890
