708
00:30:35,540 --> 00:30:37,330
Hidden bells have also been placed around the forest.

709
00:30:37,330 --> 00:30:38,430
If there's any movement,

710
00:30:38,430 --> 00:30:40,230
the bells will ring as a warning.

711
00:30:40,300 --> 00:30:41,150
Well done.

712
00:30:42,170 --> 00:30:42,780
Also,

713
00:30:42,910 --> 00:30:43,910
add more manpower

714
00:30:44,010 --> 00:30:45,650
