832
00:40:39,090 --> 00:40:40,150
You found the herb?

833
00:40:41,020 --> 00:40:42,210
Let me see.

834
00:40:46,120 --> 00:40:47,440
Look, is this it?

835
00:40:49,980 --> 00:40:50,590
That's right.

836
00:40:50,590 --> 00:40:51,510
This is it.

837
00:41:06,270 --> 00:41:07,120
Mu.

838
00:41:07,150 --> 00:41:10,860
What does that herb you used for cooking look like?

839
00:41:10,910 --> 00:41:12,300
Where did you get it?

840
00:41:12,700 --> 00:41:13,370
What?

841
00:41:13,630 --> 00:41:15,060
You want to try it again?

842
00:41:16,640 --> 00:41:17,750
No, no.

843
00:41:18,500 --> 00:41:19,300
Of course not.

844
00:41:23,290 --> 00:41:23,880
You,

845
00:41:24,260 --> 00:41:24,990
come with me.

846
00:41:32,670 --> 00:41:33,910
Eleven, here.

847
00:41:33,990 --> 00:41:34,590
Okay.

848
00:41:47,430 --> 00:41:49,550
What's your real purpose of coming to Cloud City?

849
00:41:49,550 --> 00:41:51,430
You've already hurt Ruofei once.

850
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:53,990
I won't allow it to happen again.

851
00:41:54,310 --> 00:41:55,440
I came here this time

852
00:41:55,850 --> 00:41:56,510
to stay

853
00:41:56,510 --> 00:41:58,230
by Ruofei's side

854
00:41:58,730 --> 00:42:00,490
and prevent her from getting hurt again.

855
00:42:00,490 --> 00:42:02,280
It was because you didn't believe her

856
00:42:02,280 --> 00:42:03,390
that she was wrongfully imprisoned

857
00:42:03,390 --> 00:42:05,230
and expelled from the Symphony Workshop.

858
00:42:05,230 --> 00:42:06,830
Now you tell me you're here to protect her?

859
00:42:06,830 --> 00:42:08,840
I've never doubted her.

860
00:42:09,680 --> 00:42:11,660
It's just there wasn't enough evidence at that time.

861
00:42:11,660 --> 00:42:14,320
We couldn't conclude it was Su Ruoshan's doing.

862
00:42:18,990 --> 00:42:19,990
What about the arranged marriage then?

863
00:42:19,990 --> 00:42:22,900
The arranged marriage was my father's doing.

864
00:42:23,580 --> 00:42:25,030
He had his own considerations.

865
00:42:25,030 --> 00:42:26,710
I argued with him about it later,

866
00:42:26,710 --> 00:42:28,310
but it didn't lead anywhere.

867
00:42:29,490 --> 00:42:30,760
So according to you,

868
00:42:30,780 --> 00:42:32,080
all the mistakes were made by others,

869
00:42:32,080 --> 00:42:33,390
and you have nothing to do with anything, is that right?

870
00:42:33,390 --> 00:42:33,740
No.

871
00:42:33,990 --> 00:42:35,360
Of course I made my own mistakes.

872
00:42:35,360 --> 00:42:37,270
My mistake was that I only cared about myself

873
00:42:37,270 --> 00:42:39,070
and ignored Ruofei's feelings.

874
00:42:40,150 --> 00:42:41,270
I always thought

875
00:42:41,730 --> 00:42:43,190
that as long as she left me,

876
00:42:43,620 --> 00:42:45,380
she could stay away from those dangers.

877
00:42:45,380 --> 00:42:46,240
What dangers?

878
00:42:46,900 --> 00:42:48,930
Mr. Jin, you've been in this world for a long time.

879
00:42:48,930 --> 00:42:49,990
Things like struggling for power and status

880
00:42:49,990 --> 00:42:51,230
and brothers turning against each other

881
00:42:51,230 --> 00:42:52,590
shouldn't be new to you.

882
00:42:52,900 --> 00:42:54,630
If Ruofei had stayed by my side,

883
00:42:55,000 --> 00:42:56,800
she could have been implicated.

884
00:42:57,400 --> 00:42:59,330
That's why I chose to let her leave.

885
00:42:59,830 --> 00:43:01,630
Then why did you come to find her?

886
00:43:01,840 --> 00:43:02,910
To be honest,

887
00:43:03,350 --> 00:43:04,350
before I came,

888
00:43:04,370 --> 00:43:07,060
I had already resigned from my position as Young Lord to His Majesty,

889
00:43:07,060 --> 00:43:08,420
and I turned down the arranged marriage.

890
00:43:08,420 --> 00:43:11,260
I just want to be by her side,

891
00:43:11,840 --> 00:43:13,500
even if as an ordinary person.

892
00:43:14,430 --> 00:43:16,030
This is the future I wish for.

893
00:43:16,900 --> 00:43:18,700
If you don't believe me, Mr. Jin,

894
00:43:24,390 --> 00:43:25,830
you can kill me right now.

895
00:43:38,060 --> 00:43:39,820
I can trust you this once.

896
00:43:40,210 --> 00:43:41,360
But if I find out

897
00:43:41,360 --> 00:43:43,100
that you're hiding anything from me,

898
00:43:43,100 --> 00:43:44,500
I won't let you go easily.

899
00:43:45,050 --> 00:43:46,110
Thank you, Mr. Jin.

900
00:43:46,660 --> 00:43:48,010
You don't need to thank me.

901
00:43:48,010 --> 00:43:49,610
Even if you had your reasons,

902
00:43:49,840 --> 00:43:50,830
you can't undo

903
00:43:50,830 --> 00:43:52,370
the pain you caused Su Ruofei.

904
00:43:52,370 --> 00:43:54,430
She may seem carefree on the outside,

905
00:43:54,630 --> 00:43:56,360
but when her feelings are hurt,

906
00:43:56,430 --> 00:43:57,990
she doesn't forgive easily.

907
00:43:57,990 --> 00:43:59,920
I understand everything you said.

908
00:44:00,550 --> 00:44:03,150
It was only when she really left that I realized

909
00:44:03,170 --> 00:44:04,670
nothing in this vast world,

910
00:44:04,670 --> 00:44:06,230
could compare to her smile.

911
00:44:06,830 --> 00:44:08,710
As long as I can be by her side,

912
00:44:09,610 --> 00:44:11,620
even if it's just to help her carry instruments,

913
00:44:11,620 --> 00:44:13,060
or be a small attendant,

914
00:44:13,640 --> 00:44:14,220
I'm willing to do it.

915
00:44:14,220 --> 00:44:15,360
I didn't expect that

916
00:44:15,360 --> 00:44:18,220
Little Devil's feelings for you are quite sincere.

917
00:44:20,060 --> 00:44:21,500
So what?

918
00:44:21,960 --> 00:44:24,240
In this world, sincerity without trust

919
00:44:24,280 --> 00:44:25,230
means nothing.

920
00:44:25,940 --> 00:44:28,400
Moreover, he's still the one from back then.

921
00:44:30,210 --> 00:44:31,650
Even more unforgivable.

922
00:44:34,870 --> 00:44:35,340
Wait.

923
00:44:35,380 --> 00:44:36,650
What do you mean by "the one from back then"?
